text: Hannibal is the surname of: * Abram Petrovich Gannibal or Hannibal (1697–1781), African prince and Russian general * Ivan Gannibal (1735–1801), Russian general and Abram's son * Heinrich Hannibal (1889–1971), German World War II SS officer * Robin Hannibal (), Danish and musician and record producer
title: Hannibal (surname)
